snippet.title: State of Emergency (Rockstar Games) - Full Game Longplay Walkthrough [PS2, Xbox and PC]
snippet.description:
Full longplay / playthrough of the revolution mode of the game State of Emergency (no commentaries). State of Emergency was released by Rockstar Games in 2002 for Playstation 2, Xbox and PC. PS2 version emulated in HD with PCSX2.
Support the channel on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/neogamertvga
